title: About me
text:
Hi, I’m Ewelina! I started my data analytics journey in 2022, when I developed interests in using R to optimise working on my postgraduate statistics assignments.
In my free time I particularly enjoy solving Tidy Tuesday challenges.

title: Three reasons for changing career from psychology to data analytics
text:
Despite having a Bachelor of Science and Master of Science in Psychology, last year I decided to change my career focus from pursuing psychological practice to focus on solving data challenges.
Here are the three WHYs:

Optimising workload

While psychology students are often advised to rely on using IBM SPSS in early stages of their education, many seem confused by this matter (including some of my course mates!).
